                            <h1><span class="text-orange">Hearing</span> &amp; submission choreography</h1>
                            <p class="mx-lg-0">Proportionate written rounds, simultaneous / sequential disclosures, tribunal-directed expert evidence, guarded cross-examination online, objections handling, interpreters, and clerking minutes — BharatNyay’s hearing module aligns with UNCITRAL’s notes on virtual integrity.</p>
