                    <section class="bn-about-body">
                        <div class="container bn-prose bn-prose-wide">
                            <ol class="bn-step-list">
                                <li>Pre-hearing bundles locked with hash metadata for tamper-awareness.</li>
                                <li>Live technical checks + bandwidth declarations stored with consent.</li>
                                <li>Recording policy signed by representatives before gavel metaphorically drops.</li>
                                <li>Post-hearing written submissions routed with tribunal-set deadlines.</li>
                            </ol>
